0.9.name: wordpress/tpsunrise
0.9.description: tpSunrise is a 3 column theme with a vertical menu on the left. The theme supports a widgetized sidebar on right and a flexible center column that automatically adjusts for the window width. The theme supports different header and sidebar styles for the home page. Requires WordPress 3.0+
